  <h2 id="operation">How Does a Diesel Centrifuge Work?</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start mb-6">
    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-diesel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-MOPX205-Diesel-Centrifuge-Occidental-300x300-1.webp"
